overview: Employees at Wet Warehouse get great benefits, and then some! New manager Joe Romero is warmly received by Max Stone and Shane Colt. Owner Max Grand tests some product with boink-buddy Cort Stevens. Finally, the shipping department gets into the act when Dino Phillips, Troy Steele, Joe Romero, Chad Conners and Mike Llamas increase output as they put out the many fires down below. Wet Warehouse is drenching with hot sex!
title: Wet Warehouse
